Interface CmtOnByteArray

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CmtElGamalHashCommitter, CmtElGamalHashReceiver, CmtElGamalOnByteArrayCommitter, CmtElGamalOnByteArrayReceiver, CmtPedersenHashCommitter, CmtPedersenHashReceiver

    public interface CmtOnByteArray
    Marker interface. Each committer/receiver that implement this interface is marked as committer/receiver that commit on a byte array.
